&lt;/section&gt;&lt;h4 id="membership"&gt;Membership&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The membership of the Green Construction Board represents both Government and senior representatives from industry and is jointly chaired by the Minister of State, Rt Hon Michael Fallon MP, who will act as the Government co-Chair together with Mike Putnam, President and CEO Skanska UK. DECC, Defra, DCLG, Cabinet Office and BIS are among the key Departments represented on the Group:&lt;/p&gt;

