&lt;/table&gt;&lt;h2 id="trade-association-forum"&gt;Trade Association Forum&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BIS works with the &lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.taforum.org/"&gt;Trade Association Forum&lt;/a&gt; to develop and communicate best practice among trade associations. The Forum carries out benchmarking studies and other research projects. It disseminates the results of these, and broader best practice, through its seminars, workshops and other events, and via its website.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Further information is available from:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class="address"&gt;&lt;div class="adr org fn"&gt;&lt;p&gt;

Stuart Bean
&lt;br&gt;Trade Association Forum
&lt;br&gt;Centre Point
&lt;br&gt;103 New Oxford Street 
&lt;br&gt;London WC1A 1DU
&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Telephone: 020 7395 8283
Email: &lt;a href="mailto:stuart.bean@taforum.org.uk"&gt;stuart.bean@taforum.org.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id="bis-contacts"&gt;BIS Contacts&lt;/h3&gt;
