&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ring Fence Corporation Tax&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Supplementary Charge&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Petroleum Revenue Tax&lt;/li&gt;
